{
  "stem": "26765.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so, those people had special status because the Germans thought perhaps they could use some of these people in exchange for hostages.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the, the star camp, we starved just as much, but we were able to keep our own clothes, and the-- which was very important.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, to walk around with, with that striped suit, that totally de-personalizes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So our own rags were still something that we treasured.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also, the fact that the families could stay together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, I was with George.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And later on, I was in the same barrack with George, in the mens' barrack.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, the conditions in Bergen-Belsen were indescribable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got some, some very sweet tea or coffee in the mornings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then a little rutabaga soup, just water, at Noon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then in the evening, we got the treasured piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And like I say, it would have been very easy to snatch that piece of bread from me, but no one ever did.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I find that very remarkable, considering that I can't ride public transportation in Chicago, or here in Los Angeles, with a little chain around my neck for fear somebody might grab it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "These were starving people, and a crumb of bread meant the difference between life and death.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It would have been very easy to snatch that bread from me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "No one ever did, not my brother, none of-- no one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I find that-- I just find that remarkable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, people always ask me that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What did you do there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't do much.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
